children.subject: Yes, apps are still being accepted!
Are positions still available? I just applied.

history.content:
Interested in making an impact on the DeCal program? Want hands-on experience working on a website used by thousands of DeCal students each semester? The DeCal Board is opening up applications for our web internship this fall!

Working under our webmaster, you will have the opportunity to:

- Maintain our website through content updates, new features, and bug fixes

- Get practical UX and UI experience writing copy and creating wireframes for our site

- Manage our automated mailing system

- Develop curriculum and documentation practices for future web staff

Experience with the Ruby on Rails framework, CSS + HTML, software repositories and SSH, integrations through MailChimp, SendGrid, or Google Docs, or backend dev in general are huge +s. That being said, please don't hesitate to apply if you lack prior experience— we are primarily looking for initiative and a willingness to learn! Join us as we create a community and help run the 150+ DeCals taught each semester :)

DeCal Board Application

Best,
Your friends at the DeCal Board
